The paper presents a system for optimization using a cooperative group of agents, which is a common topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE). The use of embedded search heuristics and algorithm portfolio design suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and distributed computing (cs.DC). Additionally, the optimization of constrained problems and the potential for a passive group leader suggest a connection to control systems (cs.SY).
